concentratorMode.name: concentratorMode
concentratorMode.description: This variable controls the ring mode of the chassis.

concentratorManagement.name: concentratorManagement
concentratorManagement.description: This variable controls the ability to manage token ring concentrators.

concentratorBuildTopology.name: concentratorBuildTopology
concentratorBuildTopology.description: This variable causes the chassis token ring topology database to be constructed.

concentratorTopologyLastBuild.name: concentratorTopologyLastBuild
concentratorTopologyLastBuild.description: This variable contains the value of sysUpTime at the time the chassis token ring topology database was last constructed.

concentratorChassisRingDefaults.name: concentratorChassisRingDefaults
concentratorChassisRingDefaults.description: This variable causes the chassis ring area of NVS to be set to defaults.

concentratorSlotTable.name: concentratorSlotTable
concentratorSlotTable.description: Table of descriptive and status information about a Token Ring Concentrator.

concentratorSlotEntry.name: concentratorSlotEntry
concentratorSlotEntry.description: An entry in the table containing information about a specific concentrator.

concentratorSlotIndex.name: concentratorSlotIndex
concentratorSlotIndex.description: This variable identifies the slot of the chassis.

concentratorSlotIOType.name: concentratorSlotIOType
concentratorSlotIOType.description: This variable represents the type of the I/O card.

concentratorSlotIOFirmwareVersion.name: concentratorSlotIOFirmwareVersion
concentratorSlotIOFirmwareVersion.description: This variable represents the revision level of the firmware on the I/O card.

concentratorSlotIOOperStatus.name: concentratorSlotIOOperStatus
concentratorSlotIOOperStatus.description: This variable represents the current operating status of the I/O card.

concentratorSlotUptime.name: concentratorSlotUptime
concentratorSlotUptime.description: This variable contains the value of sysUpTime at the time the concentrator was last reset.

concentratorSlotNumPorts.name: concentratorSlotNumPorts
concentratorSlotNumPorts.description: This variable represents the number of Token Ring ports supported by the concentrator.

concentratorSlotRingTable.name: concentratorSlotRingTable
concentratorSlotRingTable.description: Table of descriptive and status information about the rings of a controller.

concentratorSlotRingEntry.name: concentratorSlotRingEntry
concentratorSlotRingEntry.description: An entry in the table containing information about a specific ring.

concentratorSlotSlotIndex.name: concentratorSlotSlotIndex
concentratorSlotSlotIndex.description: This variable identifies the slot of the chassis.

concentratorSlotRingIndex.name: concentratorSlotRingIndex
concentratorSlotRingIndex.description: This variable identifies the ring within the slot.

concentratorSlotRingAdminName.name: concentratorSlotRingAdminName
concentratorSlotRingAdminName.description: This variable represents the user defined name of the ring.

concentratorSlotRingAdminSpeed.name: concentratorSlotRingAdminSpeed
concentratorSlotRingAdminSpeed.description: This variable represents the user defined speed of the ring.

concentratorSlotRingAdminState.name: concentratorSlotRingAdminState
concentratorSlotRingAdminState.description: This variable defines whether the slot ring is to be inserted into the defined chassis ring or is to be isolated.

concentratorSlotRingZero.name: concentratorSlotRingZero
concentratorSlotRingZero.description: This variable is used to control the slot ring's counters. The agent always returns 'ready' for this value. Setting the value to 'ready' has no effect.

concentratorSlotRingSinceZero.name: concentratorSlotRingSinceZero
concentratorSlotRingSinceZero.description: This variable reflects the number of time ticks since the counters were last zeroed. This variable is set to zero when concentratoSlotRingZero is written with the value 2

concentratorSlotRingChassisRing.name: concentratorSlotRingChassisRing
concentratorSlotRingChassisRing.description: This variable represents the chassis ring into which the slot ring is to be inserted if it is to be inserted.

concentratorSlotRingOperName.name: concentratorSlotRingOperName
concentratorSlotRingOperName.description: This variable represents the name currently being used to identify the slot ring. If inserted, this name will be the user defined name of the chassis ring into which it is inserted. If isolated, this name will be the user defined name of the slot ring.

concentratorSlotRingOperSpeed.name: concentratorSlotRingOperSpeed
concentratorSlotRingOperSpeed.description: This variable represents the current speed of the slot ring. If inserted, this speed will be the user defined speed of the chassis ring into which it is inserted. If isolated, this speed will be the user defined speed of the slot ring.

concentratorSlotRingOperState.name: concentratorSlotRingOperState
concentratorSlotRingOperState.description: This variable indicates whether the slot ring is inserted into the defined chassis ring or is isolated.

concentratorSlotRingChassisRingsAllowed.name: concentratorSlotRingChassisRingsAllowed
concentratorSlotRingChassisRingsAllowed.description: The list of chassis rings into which this slot ring may be inserted. The OCTET STRING contains a bit map, with a bit for 'none' (indicating it may be isolated) and one bit for each chassis ring, and enough octets for all chassis rings. The high order bit of the first octet corresponds to 'none' and each subsequent bit in ascending order corresponds to the chassis rings in order beginning with A.

concentratorChassisRingTable.name: concentratorChassisRingTable
concentratorChassisRingTable.description: Table of descriptive and status information about the rings of a the chassis.

concentratorChassisRingEntry.name: concentratorChassisRingEntry
concentratorChassisRingEntry.description: An entry in the table containing information about a specific ring.

concentratorChassisRingIndex.name: concentratorChassisRingIndex
concentratorChassisRingIndex.description: This variable identifies the ring of the chassis.

concentratorChassisRingName.name: concentratorChassisRingName
concentratorChassisRingName.description: This variable represents the name of the ring. All segments of a given chassis ring will have the same base name, All segment of that ring will appear as 'baseNamex' where x is the identified segment

concentratorChassisRingSpeed.name: concentratorChassisRingSpeed
concentratorChassisRingSpeed.description: This variable indicates the speed of the ring segment. All segments of a given chassis ring are at the same speed.

concentratorChassisRingTopologyChanges.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyChanges
concentratorChassisRingTopologyChanges.description: This variable reflects the number of times the topology has changed for this ring. This variable is set to zero when concentratorChassisRingZero is written with the value 2.

concentratorChassisRingZero.name: concentratorChassisRingZero
concentratorChassisRingZero.description: This variable is used to control the ring's counters. The agent always returns 'ready' for this value. Setting the value to 'ready' has no effect.

concentratorChassisRingSinceZero.name: concentratorChassisRingSinceZero
concentratorChassisRingSinceZero.description: This variable reflects the number of time ticks since the counters were last zeroed. This variable is set to zero when concentratoChassisRingZero is written with the value 2

concentratorChassisRingTopologyTable.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyTable
concentratorChassisRingTopologyTable.description: Table of descriptive and status information about the segments of the chassis rings.

concentratorChassisRingTopologyEntry.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyEntry
concentratorChassisRingTopologyEntry.description: An entry in the table containing information about a specific ring segment.

concentratorChassisRingTopologySlotIndex.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologySlotIndex
concentratorChassisRingTopologySlotIndex.description: This variable identifies a slot number that is included in the ring segment.

concentratorChassisRingTopologyRingIndex.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyRingIndex
concentratorChassisRingTopologyRingIndex.description: This variable identifies the ring of the chassis.

concentratorChassisRingTopologyWrapUp.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyWrapUp
concentratorChassisRingTopologyWrapUp.description: This variable represents the upper wrap state for the chassis ring which passes through this slot. By setting this variable to Wrap, the user can create a segment which would contain this slot, and all slots above this one which are on the same segment.

concentratorChassisRingTopologyWrapDown.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyWrapDown
concentratorChassisRingTopologyWrapDown.description: This variable represents the lower wrap state for the chassis ring which passes through this slot. By setting this variable to Wrap, the user can create a segment which would contain this slot, and all slots below this one which are on the same segment.

concentratorChassisRingTopologyUpState.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyUpState
concentratorChassisRingTopologyUpState.description: This variable represents the type of upper wrap for the chassis ring which passes through this slot.

concentratorChassisRingTopologyDownState.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyDownState
concentratorChassisRingTopologyDownState.description: This variable represents the type of lower wrap for the chassis ring which passes through this slot.

concentratorChassisRingTopologySegment.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologySegment
concentratorChassisRingTopologySegment.description: This variable represents the segment number for the chassis ring which passes through this slot.

concentratorChassisRingTopologyName.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyName
concentratorChassisRingTopologyName.description: This variable represents the name of the ring segment. The ring segment name is the base ring name with '-segment number' appended to the end.

concentratorChassisRingTopologySpeed.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologySpeed
concentratorChassisRingTopologySpeed.description: This variable indicates the speed of the ring segment. All segments of a given chassis ring are at the same speed as the parent ring.

concentratorChassisRingTopologyCardType.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyCardType
concentratorChassisRingTopologyCardType.description: This variable represents the type of the I/O card.

concentratorChassisRingTopologyAutoUpCha.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyAutoUpChanges
concentratorChassisRingTopologyAutoUpCha.description: This variable reflects the number of times the topology has changed for this ring due to a dynamic wrap up. This variable is set to zero when concentratorSlotRingZero is written with the value 2.

concentratorChassisRingTopologyAutoDownC.name: concentratorChassisRingTopologyAutoDownChanges
concentratorChassisRingTopologyAutoDownC.description: This variable reflects the number of times the topology has changed for this ring due to a dynamic wrap down. This variable is set to zero when concentratorSlotRingZero is written with the value 2.

concentratorPortTable.name: concentratorPortTable
concentratorPortTable.description: Table of information and status concerning the ports of a concentrator.

concentratorPortEntry.name: concentratorPortEntry
concentratorPortEntry.description: An entry in the table containing control and status information for a port.

concentratorPortSlotIndex.name: concentratorPortSlotIndex
concentratorPortSlotIndex.description: This variable identifies the slot of the chassis.

concentratorPortName.name: concentratorPortName
concentratorPortName.description: This variable represents the user defined name of the port.

concentratorPortType.name: concentratorPortType
concentratorPortType.description: This variable represents the type of connector provided for the port.

concentratorPortZero.name: concentratorPortZero
concentratorPortZero.description: This variable is used to control the ports counters. The agent always returns 'ready' for this value. Setting the value to 'ready' has no effect.

concentratorPortSinceZero.name: concentratorPortSinceZero
concentratorPortSinceZero.description: This variable reflects the number of time ticks since the counters were las zeroed. This variable is set to zero when concentratorPortZero is written with the value 2

concentratorPortAdminState.name: concentratorPortAdminState
concentratorPortAdminState.description: This variable reflects the enable/disable state of the port.

concentratorPortOperState.name: concentratorPortOperState
concentratorPortOperState.description: This variable reflects the enable/disable state of the port.

concentratorPortInsertions.name: concentratorPortInsertions
concentratorPortInsertions.description: This variable reflects the number of times the port was inserted into the ring.

concentratorPortInsertFailures.name: concentratorPortInsertFailures
concentratorPortInsertFailures.description: This variable reflects the number of times the port was not inserted due to a data rate mismatch.

concentratorPortAdminInsert.name: concentratorPortAdminInsert
concentratorPortAdminInsert.description: This variable reflects the desired insertion of the port. Auto indicates to insert the port into the first slot ring with a matching data rate beginning with 1.

concentratorPortOperInsert.name: concentratorPortOperInsert
concentratorPortOperInsert.description: This variable reflects the slot ring to which the port is attached.

concentratorPortSpeed.name: concentratorPortSpeed
concentratorPortSpeed.description: This variable reflects the measured speed of the port.

concentratorPortAdminLoopback.name: concentratorPortAdminLoopback
concentratorPortAdminLoopback.description: This variable reflects the whether this port will be inserted into a ring or the data loop backed.

concentratorPortStationType.name: concentratorPortStationType
concentratorPortStationType.description: This variable reflects the concentrator port type.

concentratorPortAdminTrunkInsert.name: concentratorPortAdminTrunkInsert
concentratorPortAdminTrunkInsert.description: This variable is used to control the insertion of trunk ports. When set to 'execute' the trunk port will be inserted into the ring immediately and not wait for the trunk timer to expire. The agent always returns 'ready' for this value. Setting the value to 'ready' has no effect.

concentratorPortSlotRingsAllowed.name: concentratorPortSlotRingsAllowed
concentratorPortSlotRingsAllowed.description: The list of slot rings into which this port may be inserted. The OCTET STRING contains a bit map, with a bit for 'none' (indicating it may be isolated) and one bit for each slot ring, and enough octets for all slot rings. The high order bit of the first octet corresponds to 'none' and each subsequent bit in ascending order corresponds to the slot rings in order beginning with 1.
